# Web UI: node deps + Vite build outputs. The committed webdist/index.html is an
# INERT placeholder (no hashed asset links) so `go build`/`go test` compile before any
# `pnpm build`; `make build-web` OVERWRITES it with the real bundle (index.html + assets/,
# assets/ not tracked). Never commit that generated bundle over the seed — a stale hashed
# link ships a broken UI (missing /assets/* → SPA fallback → text/html MIME error). If this
# file shows churn, reset it to the inert seed.
/web/node_modules/
/web/dist/
/internal/daemon/webdist/assets/
/.playwright-mcp/
.superpowers/
